(define/contract (maximum-strong-pair-xor nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let loop ((nums nums) (max-xor 0))
    (cond
      [(null? nums) max-xor]
      [else
       (let inner-loop ((rest (cdr nums)) (current (car nums)) (current-max-xor max-xor))
         (cond
           [(null? rest) (loop (cdr nums) current-max-xor)]
           [else
            (let ((next (car rest)))
              (when (and (<= (abs (- current next)) (min current next))
                         (> (bitwise-xor current next) current-max-xor))
                (set! current-max-xor (bitwise-xor current next)))
              (inner-loop (cdr rest) current current-max-xor))]))])))
